# Summary

This detection identifies repeated failed Windows authentication attempts that may indicate brute-force or password guessing activity.

When combined with additional detections such as successful authentication, privileged account monitoring, and remote desktop analysis, it provides an effective first layer of defense against credential-based attacks.
